title: The FDA's New Rule on Telemedicine Abortion
itunes:title: The FDA's New Rule on Telemedicine Abortion
description:
Good news, what? Recently, the US Food and Drug Administration announced a permanent repeal on the in-person dispensing on a popular medication for abortion. Bridget Todd stops by to explain what that means. 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
